ou're not gon na find some evidence -LRB- of illegality -RRB-, but you can go right over to Wall Street and find people who stole hundreds of millions of dollars,'' he said. As for <PERSON> Beck </PERSON> himself, he said he hopes to see his 100th Labor Day, `` and I plan to.'' `` But,'' he added, `` I do n't know that I'd bank on it.''
