<BYLINE>Hamadi Sought Sanctuary In Iran After TWA Hijacking
^By NESHA STARCEVIC</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>FRANKFURT, West Germany (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
