<FIRST>r i AM-Israel-Lebanon     09-06 0104</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Israel-Lebanon,0107</SECOND>
<HEAD>Guerrillas Fire Rocket At Militiamen</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-Israel, Bjt</HEAD>
<DATELINE>JERUSALEM (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
