<HEAD>Fortune Stems From Texas Oil Money</HEAD>
<BYLINE>BY KELLEY SHANNON</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>FORT WORTH, Texas (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
